asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Coach
description:
Hey Team, people call me "Coach".  
I was born in the humble burrows of Fluflanta in the rockin' 70's. My parents were working in the carrot yards trying to put lettuce on the table when both were lost in the town's infamous mining accident. I was left alone in the world and ended up mixing with some crowds that nearly took me down the wrong path. I was only hitting my teens when I discovered the power of music. I began making music with what I could find around the place. Empty pans, sticks etc etc. I was obsessed. Twelve beats a day for three summers and thus the new genre "Fluf Hop' was born. I would go on to dominate the Fluf World charts and help move Fluf Hop to the most listened to genre in the world. Along my journey I would find other Flufs that needed the guidance I had so long craved. It would result in major Fluf stars Lil Wabbit  White Hare signing to my label who have on their own gone on to dominate the music world.
These days I've settled into living in my mansion and investing in any good start ups I see arise. I'll accept paid appearances if I think the ethos of the brand is worthy of my time and I do what I can to help the younger Flufs find the right path for their life.
